/*Diligências Filtro Hipotecas*/
(SELECT sp.Id as id, FROM_UNIXTIME(floor(sact.activated/1000)) as dateCreated, sass.resourceid as resourceId, sact.Name AS Atividade, sp.Name AS Processo, dp.c_urgencia AS Urgencia, null as OrigemProcesso, dp.c_nome_banco AS NomeBanco, dp.c_n_wf_banco AS NumeroWFBanco, dp.c_n_wf_pl as NumeroWFPL, dp.c_tipo_processo as TipoProcesso, dp.c_nome_cliente as NomeCliente, c_estado_contratacao AS EstadoContratacao, sact.Id AS ActivityId, from_unixtime(sact.LimitTime/1000, '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i') as limittime, null as DataInicio, null as DataFim, ip.c_nome AS Cliente, ag.c_data_agendamento AS DataAgendamento, null as SLADuracao, interp.c_intervencao_juridica, interp.c_intervencao_juridica_novo, p.c_servico as Servico, null as DateModified, null as inicializacaoGestor, null as CategoriaProcesso, null as UrgenciaRegisto, null as EstadoAgendamento
FROM shkprocesses sp 
JOIN app_fd_info_diligencia d on sp.Id = d.c_id_diligencia
LEFT JOIN shkprocessstates sps ON sps.oid = sp.State
LEFT JOIN SHKActivities sact ON sact.ProcessId = sp.Id 
LEFT JOIN SHKActivityStates ssta ON ssta.oid = sact.State 
LEFT JOIN SHKAssignmentsTable sass ON sact.Id = sass.ActivityId 
LEFT JOIN app_fd_processos_hip p ON p.id = d.c_id_processo 
LEFT JOIN app_fd_detalhe_proce_hip dp ON dp.id = p.c_detalhe_processo
LEFT JOIN app_fd_interv_processo interp ON interp.c_id_processo = p.id
LEFT JOIN app_fd_interv_processo_hip ip ON ip.c_id_processo = p.id AND ip.c_cliente_principal = 'CHECK' 
LEFT JOIN app_fd_agendamento ag ON ag.id = p.c_agendamento
WHERE sps.KeyValue LIKE 'open.running' AND (ssta.KeyValue LIKE 'open.not_running.not_started' OR ssta.KeyValue LIKE 'open.running') 
AND IF ('#currentUser.groups.id#' LIKE '%Coordenador%' AND '#currentUser.department.id#' LIKE '%PL_INT_AO%', d.c_equipa_destinataria LIKE 'PL_INT_AO', sass.resourceid LIKE '%#currentUser.username#%')
AND d.id LIKE '%hipotecas%'
AND d.c_diligencia_prioritaria = 1)

/*Diligências Geral*/
UNION
(SELECT sp.Id as id, FROM_UNIXTIME(floor(sact.activated/1000)) as dateCreated, sass.resourceid as resourceId, sact.Name AS Atividade, sp.Name AS Processo, dp.c_urgencia AS Urgencia, dp.c_origem_processo as OrigemProcesso, dp.c_nome_banco AS NomeBanco, dp.c_n_wf_banco AS NumeroWFBanco, dp.c_n_wf_pl as NumeroWFPL, dp.c_tipo_processo as TipoProcesso, dp.c_nome_cliente as NomeCliente, c_estado_contratacao AS EstadoContratacao, sact.Id AS ActivityId, from_unixtime(sact.LimitTime/1000, '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i') as limittime, sla.c_data_inicio as DataInicio,sla.c_data_fim as DataFim, ip.c_nome AS Cliente, CONCAT(ato.c_dataOutorga, ' ', ato.c_horaOutorga) AS DataAgendamento, sla.c_duracao as SLADuracao, interp.c_intervencao_juridica, interp.c_intervencao_juridica_novo, p.c_servico as Servico, null as DateModified, dp.c_inicializacao_gestor as inicializacaoGestor, null as CategoriaProcesso, null as UrgenciaRegisto, null as EstadoAgendamento
FROM shkprocesses sp 
JOIN app_fd_info_diligencia d ON sp.Id = d.id 
LEFT JOIN shkprocessstates sps ON sps.oid = sp.State 
LEFT JOIN SHKActivities sact ON sact.ProcessId = sp.Id 
LEFT JOIN SHKActivityStates ssta ON ssta.oid = sact.State 
LEFT JOIN SHKAssignmentsTable sass ON sact.Id = sass.ActivityId 
LEFT JOIN app_fd_processos p ON p.id = d.c_id_processo 
LEFT JOIN app_fd_detalhe_processo dp ON dp.id = p.c_detalhe_processo 
LEFT JOIN app_fd_interv_processo interp ON interp.c_id_processo = p.id 
LEFT JOIN app_fd_sla_atividade sla ON sla.c_id_processo = sp.Id
LEFT JOIN app_fd_intervenientes_proc ip ON ip.c_id_processo = p.id AND ip.c_cliente_principal = 'CHECK' 
LEFT JOIN app_fd_agendamento ag ON ag.id = p.c_agendamento
LEFT JOIN app_fd_atos ato ON ato.c_id_agendamento = ag.id AND ato.c_status = 'AGD'
WHERE sps.KeyValue LIKE 'open.running' AND (ssta.KeyValue LIKE 'open.not_running.not_started' OR ssta.KeyValue LIKE 'open.running') 
AND (sla.c_estado_atividade is null or sla.c_estado_atividade = 'Em curso' or sla.c_estado_atividade = 'Pendente') 
AND IF ('#currentUser.groups.id#' LIKE '%Coordenador%' AND '#currentUser.department.id#' LIKE '%PL_INT_AO%', d.c_equipa_destinataria LIKE 'PL_INT_AO', sass.resourceid LIKE '%#currentUser.username#%')
AND d.c_diligencia_prioritaria = 1)
